title: PSP-IPΔ2: PSP Liquidity Engine “La Seine”🌊
body:
This proposal addresses liquidity on the PSP token, and propose an incentive program to sustainably grow the SushiSwap pool.

The envisioned program would allocate 5M PSP over the next 3 months; renewable by DAO vote.

It will use Alchemist's Crucible to better align stakers' incentive and provide additional convenience for depositors.

Please read the full proposal here:

https://gov.paraswap.network/t/psp-ip-2-psp-liquidity-engine-la-seine/85
